originalText.text: Was diagnosed in 2017 stage 3 and given 6 months to live upstate.  Came to see Dr Rosenberg Jan 2018. He is hands down the most caring,brilliant,and thoughtfull oncologist top notch. I would highly recommend Dr Rosenberg and MSK staff to anyone with cancer. Don't give up there are new treatments every day. You would be fortunate to have him I can't say enough good things about him.

originalText.text:
In 2005 I was diagnosed with stage 4 kidney cancer, Doctors in Brazil told me I had 3 to 6 months to live. I went to San Francisco UCSF to see Dr Rosenberg and I’m still here.
12/13/2022 Thank You Dr Jonathan Rosenberg!

originalText.text: He is simply the very best! He treated my mother from 2015 to 2018 and helped prolong her life by years and she had a good quality of life during that time. A brilliant scholar and a caring soul. You would be very lucky to be in his care.
